# CODEOWNERS — automatic reviewer assignment.
#
# Format: <path-pattern> @owner1 @owner2
# Lines are matched LAST-MATCH-WINS, so more specific patterns go later.
#
# The repo follows a single-maintainer model today. As contributors take
# stewardship of subsystems, add domain owners below their area's section.

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Default — repo-wide fallback.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*                                       @nexus

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AI vibe-coding workbench artifacts.
# Changes to rules / skills / lint / CLAUDE.md affect every contributor,
# so they explicitly route to the maintainer.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/CLAUDE.md                              @nexus
/.cursor/rules/                         @nexus
/.claude/skills/                        @nexus
/scripts/check-*                        @nexus
/.githooks/                             @nexus

